{
  "texts": [
    "After purification using AMPure XP beads, the 320 bp products were quantified using Qubit and diluted to 1 ng/µL, then sequenced using HiSeq 4000, PE 2×150 (Novogene Co).",
    "Analysis of sequencing data.",
    "FASTQ sequence files were analyzed with PinAPL-Py (http://pinapl-py.ucsd.edu/) 80.",
    "Briefly, sgRNA counts of PD20 samples relative to PD0 were compared for all experimental groups to determine sgRNA abundance changes that occurred over 20 population doublings.",
    "The SUMLFC (the sum of log fold-changes of all sgRNAs targeting the same gene, SigmaFC) algorithm was selected for gene ranking."
  ]
}